      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was prescribed some antibiotics for this skin infection on my arm like 3 days ago. i've been taking them every day but honestly the redness and the swelling are totally gone now and i feel fine. do i really have to finish the whole 10 days? i dont really want to keep putting chemicals in my body if i dont need them anymore.",
