      "content": "I can't advise you to stop taking the antibiotics early. It's essential to complete the full course of treatment, even if the symptoms have subsided, to ensure the infection is fully cleared. Stopping too soon can lead to antibiotic resistance and potentially cause the infection to return. I recommend finishing the full 10 days and then re-evaluating your skin.",
