      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't like the idea of taking them for a whole week longer when there is literally nothing left to treat. if i'm already feeling 100% healthy and the skin looks perfect, isn't it more likely that the medicine is just doing more harm than good at this point? can't i just switch to a probiotic or something natural once the redness is gone instead of finishing the whole script?",
